description: Arbitrary person-level identifier. Used to link across tables.
Arbitrary identifier for each unique address record.
Longitude assigned to the address by the geocoding algorithm. WGS84 format.
Latitude assigned to the address by the geocoding algorithm. WGS84 format.
Census Block associated with the address.
Census Tract associated with the address.
Census Block Group associated with the address.
Zip code tabulation area associated with the address.
Field that can be used to store a custom/local geocode for a given address.
Text description of the terminology/approach used to assign the custom geocode.
Name of shapefile used in the geocoding process.
Level of accuracy of the geocoded address based on the method used.
Reference to the methodology/software and parameters used to assign the geocode.
Date that the geocoding was completed.
